    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rooms in which cloaks, coats, hats, or other outerwear garments may be placed, usually located near the entrance of a place of assembly and intended for short-term placement of the garments. The term may also refer to a space located in railway-stations, other transportation stations, or hotel, where luggage of any description is temporarily taken charge of.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
